their journeys together.<br>
I know I haven't yet written the storyline behind Tanj and I meeting in game, or the Vah Shir only wedding (we're still planning a 'guild wedding' to marry us both to The Edgers), however, I couldn't resist putting this up 'early' <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   )<br>
